{"ja420:0.1":"Jataka ","ja420:0.2":"Atthakanipata ","ja420:0.3":"Kaccanivagga ","ja420:0.4":"4. Sumangalajataka ","ja420:1.1":"“Bhusamhi kuddhoti avekkhiyana, ","ja420:1.2":"Na tava dandam panayeyya issaro; ","ja420:1.3":"Atthanaso appatirupamattano, ","ja420:1.4":"Parassa dukkhani bhusam udiraye. ","ja420:2.1":"Yato ca janeyya pasadamattano, ","ja420:2.2":"Attham niyunjeyya parassa dukkatam; ","ja420:2.3":"Tadayamatthoti sayam avekkhiya, ","ja420:2.4":"Athassa dandam sadisam nivesaye. ","ja420:3.1":"Na capi jhapeti param na attanam, ","ja420:3.2":"Amucchito yo nayate nayanayam; ","ja420:3.3":"Yo dandadharo bhavatidha issaro, ","ja420:3.4":"Sa vannagutto siriya na dhamsati. ","ja420:4.1":"Ye khattiya se anisammakarino, ","ja420:4.2":"Panenti dandam sahasa pamucchita; ","ja420:4.3":"Avannasamyuta jahanti jivitam, ","ja420:4.4":"Ito vimuttapi ca yanti duggatim. ","ja420:5.1":"Dhamme ca ye ariyappavedite rata, ","ja420:5.2":"Anuttara te vacasa manasa kammuna ca; ","ja420:5.3":"Te santisoraccasamadhisanthita, ","ja420:5.4":"Vajanti lokam dubhayam tathavidha. ","ja420:6.1":"Rajahamasmi narapamadanamissaro, ","ja420:6.2":"Sacepi kujjhami thapemi attanam; ","ja420:6.3":"Nisedhayanto janatam tathavidham, ","ja420:6.4":"Panemi dandam anukampa yoniso”. ","ja420:7.1":"“Siri ca lakkhi ca taveva khattiya, ","ja420:7.2":"Janadhipa ma vijahi kudacanam; ","ja420:7.3":"Akkodhano niccapasannacitto, ","ja420:7.4":"Anigho tuvam vassasatani palaya. ","ja420:8.1":"Gunehi etehi upeta khattiya, ","ja420:8.2":"Thitamariyavatti suvaco akodhano; ","ja420:8.3":"Sukhi anuppila pasasamedinim, ","ja420:8.4":"Ito vimuttopi ca yahi suggatim. ","ja420:9.1":"Evam sunitena subhasitena, ","ja420:9.2":"Dhammena nayena upayaso nayam; ","ja420:9.3":"Nibbapaye sankhubhitam mahajanam, ","ja420:9.4":"Mahava megho salilena medinin”ti. ","ja420:10.1":"Sumangalajatakam catuttham. "}